00:57:34.329 --> 00:57:39.660
people so that they're not other; they're
not perceived as beneath us. Anytime we don't

00:57:39.660 --> 00:57:44.240
perceive the other person as individual human,
it's very easy to be cruel, unkind, to be

00:57:44.240 --> 00:57:53.640
oppressive as we see around the world every
